      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">January 28th 1885 ¶ Baron Von Mueller C.M.G., M. &amp; Ph.D., &amp;c. ¶ Government Botanist ¶ Melbourne ¶ Sir,...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">85.01.28</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Andrew Berry</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Letter press copy book 1883-6, p. 473, School of Mines and Industries, Ballarat, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">January 28th 1885</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Von Mueller C.M.G., M. &amp; Ph.D., &amp;c.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Government Botanist</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your esteemed favour of yesterday's date<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to A. Berry, 27 January 1885 (in this edition as 85-01-27b).</p>
               </note> together with the Volume of "Proceedings of the Zoological and Acclimatisation Society" kindly presented by you to The School have been duly received.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M's donation was acknowledged under 'subscriptions and donations', <seg style="font-style: italic; ">School of Mines Ballarat. Annual Report 1885</seg>, p. 55.</p>
               </note> — Pray accept the best thanks of the Council for your gift which is a very acceptable addition to the Library. We have a copy of the little volume of Popular Science Lectures similar to the one forwarded to you — in our Library — and a copy will be found in the Public Library Melbourne — and many other public institutions<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Ballaarat science lectures. First series, 1882</seg> (1883) included B83.13.05, which had been previously published as a pamphlet (B82.13.07). See also A. Berry to M, 26 January 1885.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours obediently</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Andw Berry</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Registrar</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
